2001-02-17
----------
* deleted compatibility code for old meta_tables and meta_fields
* improved cookies: path is set and script-name is encoded in cookie name, such
  that there should be no conflicts with other Gedafe applications
* app_site and app_path are not anymore used
  (wrong_url.html template is obsolete)
* gedafed: SITE accepts only one argument (url of the site)
* changed example templates to use DATABASE_DESC to make them not demo-specific
  (as suggested by Brook Milligan <brook@biology.nmsu.edu>)
* new template variable: DATABASE_DESC (COMMENT on database)
* added usage information to gedafe-ctl (daemon-ctl)

